# Plotly example
Marcus W. Beck, beck.marcus@epa.gov  


```r
library(dplyr)
library(plotly)
library(WRTDStidal)

dat <- attr(tidfitmean, 'fits') %>% 
  .[[1]] %>% 
  select(-date, -year, -month, -day) %>% 
  as.matrix

scene <- list(
  aspectmode = 'manual', 
  aspectratio = list(x = 0.5, y = 1, z = 0.3)
  )

p <- plot_ly(z = ~dat) %>% add_surface() %>% 
  layout(scene = scene)
p
```
